DataList.LocalizeJP: 前に出るタイプじゃないんだけどなぁ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'm not the type who shows myself in the frontline, though.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 必要って言うなら、やってあげるけどぉ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: If you say that it's necessary, then I'll do it for you.

DataList.LocalizeJP: …ふぅん？
だから言ったでしょぉ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: I've told you so, didn't I?

DataList.LocalizeJP: こういうのが得意な子に任せてよねぇ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Leave it to someone who's good at it, okay?

DataList.LocalizeJP: あらぁ？こんなこともするの？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Oh? You want me to do this too?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 今日は機嫌が良くて助かったわねぇ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Aren't you lucky that I'm in a good mood today?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 結構がんばったんだけど…、何かご褒美はないのかしらぁ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: I've worked hard. Shouldn't I get some praise?

DataList.LocalizeJP: できない…、とは言ってないゾ☆
DataList.LocalizeEN: I didn't say I can't do it.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 助かるわぁ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: That was helpful.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 本気にさせたいのかしら。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Are you trying to make me treat this seriously?

DataList.LocalizeJP: あらあら。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Ah.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 無駄なことをするのね？
DataList.LocalizeEN: You're doing something useless.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ま、あくまでお手伝いだし？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Well, I'm just here to help.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ちょっとだけ、やってみようかしらぁ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'll give it a try, just a little bit.

DataList.LocalizeJP: まだいるのぉ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: There's more?

DataList.LocalizeJP: …まだ終わらないのぉ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's still not over?

DataList.LocalizeJP: アリガト☆
DataList.LocalizeEN: Thank you!

DataList.LocalizeJP: はぁ、はぁ、はぁ…。
余裕力って感じの戦いだったゾ☆
DataList.LocalizeEN: It was an easy battle.

DataList.LocalizeJP: この借りは、あとで全部返してもらうわよぉ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: You gotta return all my favors later, okay?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 自分で動くタイプじゃないの。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'm not the type to take action myself.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ふぅん、本当に…、大丈夫？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Hmm, this is really okay?

DataList.LocalizeJP: ここまでするつもりはなかったけどぉ…。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I didn't intend to go this far, but...

DataList.LocalizeJP: ほんっと、しょうがないんだから。
DataList.LocalizeEN: This really can't be helped.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 結局こうなっちゃうのよねぇ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: It always ends like this, huh?

DataList.LocalizeJP: だからぁ…、言ったじゃなぁい？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Didn't I told you?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 好きにやって頂戴？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Please do as you like.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 悪くないかもぉ？…それで？私は何をすればいいのかしらぁ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: This is not bad, right? So, what should I do?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 借りは作らない主義だけどぉ…。覚えておくわね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I don't like owing people favors, but I will remember this one.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 頭がすっきりするって感じぃ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: My head feels clear?

DataList.LocalizeJP: なんだか、能力を使いやすくなったかもぉ…。ん？気になるなら試してみるぅ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Using my ability felt easier... Huh? If you're curious, do you want to give it a try?

DataList.LocalizeJP: あなたって、他の人にもこんな感じなのぉ？ふふ、これはきっと相当な人気力ね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Are you like this with other people? Fufu, you must be quite popular.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ふぅん？これも先生だからかしらぁ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Huh? I wonder if you're doing this also because you're a teacher.

DataList.LocalizeJP: たまには頭の中を覗きたいな、っと思っているのよぉ？…あ。まだやってないから心配しないでちょうだい☆
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sometimes I want to peek into your head. Ah, I haven't done it, so please don't worry.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ちょっとぉ…、よそ者相手にやりすぎじゃないかしらぁ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Hey, don't you think you've done too much for an outsider?
